{"tid":2022084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男學生身懷汽油彈 感化報告指被告有反社會人格 判監12個月","createTime":"2020-05-18T06:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T10:54:29.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"64292be6cf14e460be25e36429c6f7789b45ea07","tid":2022084,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭呢？屌那星<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男學生身懷5汽油彈在旺角警署外聚集被判監12個月<br />\n18.05.2020 13:50<br />\n<br />\n一名23歲男學生去年萬聖節，即港鐵太子站831事件兩個月，在旺角警署聚集時遭警方發現身上攜有5個汽油彈，早前承認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器，在西九龍法院被判監12個月。裁判官認為案情相當嚴重，指汽油彈殺傷力和破壞力不言而喻，不會用作自衛。<br />\n<br />\n感化官在背景報告內，指被告為掩飾身份及避免遺下指模，在一個未獲准的公眾集會，身穿黑衫及戴上黑手套，認為他守法意識識薄弱，有反社會人格。辯方不同意感化官報告，要求法庭不要接納。辯方又指，被告承認法律後果，已受到教訓，犯案不是預謀，同時無打算使用汽油彈，希望法庭輕判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288286&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288286%26csid%3D261_341&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=8c0412af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288286&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"345d36ac1d234e908a1686400811b76d9663792d","tid":2022084,"uid":63400,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:13:31.000Z","msg":"立法會已完表示： 年輕人留案底令人生更精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8da3e4ab7c1c0d5931e28d8592864579b9d35f","tid":2022084,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"提提大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Task1 Task2 Like retweet reply</span><br />\nTwitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=789351b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4